Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I stand in secret silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:18.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子(れつこ)の歌声）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I scream into the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pain never ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:22.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）あと10分で\N終了時間となります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:27.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Your time is up in ten minutes.\NWould you like to extend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:27.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,延長いたしますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あっ 終わりまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:29.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\Nこのカラオケボックスは 私の聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,These karaoke rooms are my sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:39.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A place of tranquility\Non my way home from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会社帰りの安らぎの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We await your next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）またのお越しを\Nお待ちしております
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:46.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never let anyone see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）絶対に\N誰にも見られちゃいけない―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:51.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:56.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:30.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:36.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生のかけ声）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）プロテイン！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:40.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（アシスタント）はい\N今日のヨガ講座は ここまでです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:40.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!\NThat's it for today's yoga class!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテイン！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:41.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,また来週も\Nいい汗かきましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:43.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work up a good\Nsweat again next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,痛(いて)てて…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美(わしみ)）筋肉痛？\N慣れないうちは結構ハードでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:51.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sore muscles? It's quite hard\Nif you're not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ええ まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:52.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:59.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't put on excess muscle\Nfrom training here, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:59.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ここで教わってたら 無駄に筋肉\Nついちゃったりしませんかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）どういうこと？\N（烈子）だって あの先生―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:01.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that instructor leaves\Nyoga to his assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:03.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ヨガはアシスタントに任せて―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ヨガはアシスタントに任せて―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）プロ テイン\Nプロ テイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:04.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）プロ テイン\Nプロ テイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ずーっと\N筋トレばっか やってるし―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）プロ テイン\Nプロ テイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,and all he does is muscle building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテインとしか言わないし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He keeps saying "protein".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:14.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何ていうか どう見ても\Nヨガの講師とは名ばかりの その…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\Nhe's a yoga instructor in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:14.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）筋肉バカって\N言いたいのね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,"Meat head."\NIs that what you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:21.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いえいえ\N別に そういうわけじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! I didn't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子ちゃん あの先生はね―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, he may not look it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ見えて 本場インドで\N厳しい修行を積んだ―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,he's an amazing person who went\Nthrough strict training in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,立派な方なのよ\N（先生）プロテイ～ン！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,その証拠に ほら見て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 ここに\N通うようになってから―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:36.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've been coming here,\Nmy upper arms have become so defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:36.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すっごく二の腕がスッキリしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:37.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほ～ら！\N（烈子）うわああ～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:40.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,不安にさせないでください！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not reassuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）烈子ちゃんは\N何で ヨガ始めたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you come to yoga, Retsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ あ～ え～っと…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:48.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well... You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そりゃ きれいになりたいからに\N決まってるわよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:51.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you want\Nto be beautiful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ はあ… まあ\Nそんなとこですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:55.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アハ アハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）結婚相手 見つけて\N会社 辞めるためなんて―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:03:01.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it's to help me find\Na marriage partner so I can quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,言えないよな…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）どうする？\N御飯 食べ行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?\NWant to go for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:08.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）あっ いいわね～\Nこの間行った あのお店は？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds nice! How about\Nthat restaurant we've been to before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,キッシュが おいしかったとこ\N（鷲美）あそこは もういいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the yummy quiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Grilled meat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）じゃあ 焼き肉\N（鷲美）太るじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子ちゃんも行くでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Let's go!\NThere's so much I want to hear about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:21.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ねっ 行こう\Nいろいろ 話も聞きたいし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あっ すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,帰ります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:26.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,冷蔵庫に\N片づけなきゃいけない食材―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some leftovers\Nin my fridge that I need to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,余らしちゃってて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:34.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:38.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あら… そう…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:50.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）フー… プロテイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:58.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田(だ)）烈子ってさあ 何か\N壁作ってくるとこ あるよなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:58.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko... it seems\Nthat she's ignoring us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子(こ)）まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's refused to go out with us\Nthree times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,３回連続で\N飲み会 断られると―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,さすがに心 折れるわ ハア～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got me down...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:06.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,その度に\Nハイ田の やけ酒に―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about how I feel\Nhaving to accompany you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,つきあわされる\Nこっちの身にもなってよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,every time you go to drown your sorrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何なんだよ 烈子の“用事”って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping Retsuko so busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まさか男とかじゃねえだろうな？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Not some man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多分 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:17.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それ 烈子に聞いたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Retsuko tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの子 自分のこと\Nあんまり話さないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:26.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't talk a lot about herself.\NAnd I don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私も聞かないし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ただの憶測ってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're just guessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:29.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,推理だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,An educated guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,STARTING MY YOGA CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,誰だよ？ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:39.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）\N知らない人が\Nヨガ教室で撮った写真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a picture that someone\Ntook in their yoga class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the person in\Nthe background looks like Retsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,後ろに写ってるの\N烈子っぽくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子って会社を出たら\N普通 駅に直行すんの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko normally goes\Nstraight to the station after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:54.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 週に２回だけ\N駅の反対方向に向かうんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:54.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But twice a week,\Nshe heads in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,つまり 会社近辺の\Nどっかに通ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going somewhere\Nnear the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's twice a week so it's\Nprobably some kind of lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それが週に２回\N習い事の可能性大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,最近 筋肉痛を訴えてたから\N恐らく 体使う系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:04.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been feeling sore lately,\Nso it must be something physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,スポーツジムって\Nキャラじゃないから―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:09.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's not the gym type,\NI guessed it was either Pilates or yoga,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:10.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ピラティスとかヨガとかかなって\N当たりつけて 検索かけたら―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:13.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,and when I searched,\NI found this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,その写真がヒット
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,怖(こえ)えよ お前\N敵に回したくねえわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to be your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,しょうがないじゃん\N烈子が話してくんないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:20.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be done.\NRetsuko wasn't going to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）せっかく誘ってくれたのに\N断っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:32.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,They were kind to invite me,\Nbut I turned them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,２人と知り合いになれて\Nうれしかったけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:35.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I became\Nacquaintances with them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり 会社の人なんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,They're people from\Nthe office, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いろいろ聞かれても面倒だし…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be awkward\Nbeing asked some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:46.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はあ～あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ヤギュウの力み声）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ヤギュウ）駄目だ…\N（大上(おおかみ)）あ 俺やるっす
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:05:59.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:06.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ふっ… うお… かってえ\Nマジ開かねっすよ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:06.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tight! I really can't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,坪根(つぼね)の開かずの つくだ煮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsubone's unopenable jars."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:10.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,まだ開いてなかったのか あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,So she still hasn't opened it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根）あら～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:19.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子さん\Nちょうどいいとこに来たわ～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:23.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,悪いけど このつくだ煮の瓶\N開けてもらってもいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you open this jar for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ものすご～く固いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:27.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind you, it's really tightly sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと頑張り屋さんの\Nあなたなら できるわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure a go-getter\Nlike you would be able to....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,きっと頑張り屋さんの\Nあなたなら できるわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ふたが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:30.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ふたが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あっ 開きました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!\NI opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）烈子 お前すげえな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, you're really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ 何で？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:49.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You were like King Arthur back there.\NHave you taken up body building?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アーサー王みたいだったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:50.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ボディービルでも始めたのか？\N（烈子）え～？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:54.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,おかしいな 確かに\Nヨガ教室の写真に写ってたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:54.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. It was\Ndefinitely a photo from a yoga class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何の話？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Is something wrong?\N-No, just thinking out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いやいや こっちの話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:06.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）こないだのこと\N怒ってるのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they angry that\NI turned them down the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,次 会ったら ちゃんと謝ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see them,\NI'll apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:29.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり 烈子ちゃん\N私たちのこと 嫌ってるのかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:30.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Retsuko really\Ndoes hate us after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリの泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\N一回 断られただけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She just declined once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,また今度 誘ってみましょ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:36.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try inviting her again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生のかけ声）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:17.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテイ～ン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:17.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（アシスタント）はい\N今日のヨガ講座は ここまでです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for today's yoga class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:20.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）プロテイ～ン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（アシスタント）また来週も\Nいい汗かきましょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work up a good\Nsweat again next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お疲れさまです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Another good class today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:35.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）あっ はい\Nありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテイ～ン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:54.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）烈子ちゃ～ん\N駅まで一緒に行こ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:54.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko!\NLet's go to the station together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれっ 今日は\Nどこも寄らないんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're not\Nstopping anywhere today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん 今日は帰るだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Today we're just going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:06.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こないだは すみません\Nせっかく誘ってくれたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:06.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the other day,\Nturning down your invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! Water under the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:11.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいのよ～ そんなこと\Nぜ～んぜん気にしてないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\N烈子ちゃん 何線で帰るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:14.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, what line do you take?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ 田園都市線です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Den-en-toshi line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Which line do you two take?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お二人は どちらに帰るんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:23.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）あ～ああ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE\NRECEPTION 2ND FLOOR
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああああああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,カラオケ 最近 行ってな～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done karaoke in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.12,0:09:31.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はっ\N（鷲美）私も行ってな～い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither have I!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:33.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ええっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:33.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:35.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）あら？\N鷲美 もしかして―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:37.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Washimi, do you feel\Nlike singing, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,歌いたい気分？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも ゴリちゃん 帰るのよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Gori, we were going home, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:46.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしよっか～？\N中 見てから 決めよっか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say...\NShall we check it out and decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）見るだけ見てみよっか～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ えっ ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いらっしゃいませ お一人様…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. Party of one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,三名様ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A room for three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:03.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said you were\Njust going home today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:03.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今日は帰るって\N言ったじゃないですか～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子の泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,カラオケ久しぶり～\N（鷲美）わりと きれいじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rather nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ･鷲美）烈子ちゃん\Nカラオケって よく来るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you do karaoke often, Retsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いえ 私は あまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,とりあえず何か飲み物 頼もっか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we order\Nsome drinks for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はいっ ビールの人～？\N（鷲美）はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:27.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）２人のペースに\N巻き込まれないようにしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be drawn into their trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ 私 ウーロン茶で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'll have Oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:33.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ビール ビール ウーロン茶ね\N了解～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:33.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Two beers and a cup of tea. Copy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）フロントです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:39.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Two beers and an Oolong cocktail, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ：小声）ビール２杯と\Nウーロンハイ お願いしまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）アルコール混入事件 発生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's spiking the tea with alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\Nそんなに緊張することないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:52.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会社の外では 上司も先輩もないわ\N同じ女同士でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside work, there's no office hierarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そうよ 私たち…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:57.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're... yoga buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ヨガダチなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ヨガダチ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoga buddies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends on a journey of self-discovery,\Nopening chakras,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ヨガを通じて 己を見つめ直し―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,チャクラを開いて 宇宙と\N一体となることを共に目指す仲間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:09.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,and becoming one with the universe\Ntogether! That's yoga buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:09.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それが ヨガダチ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）いや 私 そんな\N大それたこと 考えてませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's that big a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）心を自由になさい\N（エコー）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Free your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:18.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）とりあえず… 歌おっか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,イエーイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:23.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ううう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Retsuko's going\Nto sing for us. I'm really curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子ちゃん\N何歌ってくれるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,超興味ある～！\N（鷲美）意外にヒップホップ系とか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Some old-school hip-hop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アイドル系じゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Or some J-pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ 私 デス系です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm into death metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\Nなんて言えるわけないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:38.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,なんとか\Nこの場を乗り切らないと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get through this somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:42.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あっ 私 あんまり\Nレパートリー ないんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much of a repertoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ これ サビしか歌えないな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I only know the chorus of this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ 時間もったいないんで どうぞ\N先輩たちから歌ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:48.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm wasting our time.\NYou two please sing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We have three hours,\Ntake your time and choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,３時間あるから\Nゆっくり選びなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）長期戦に持ち込まれた…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dragged into a long battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought your beer\Nand the Oolong cocktail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）ビールとウーロンハイ\Nお持ちしました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:02.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えーと これも駄目だな\Nこれ 歌詞が中二すぎるしな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this one...\NThis one's too teenage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This is out of my range.\NThis one is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これ多分 キーが合わないな これは\Nギャラリーが引きそうだしな…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）なかなか手ごわいわね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:09.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the type of girl\Nwho is always on her toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多分\N壁を作っちゃうタイプの子なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫 先生は おっしゃったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NThe instructor told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（先生）プロテイ～ン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,このメモが\N私たちを―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:18.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This note will guide\Nus to the right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,正しい答えに\N導いてくれると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）何なの？ その数字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that number?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）分からない…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:22.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:28.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,一体 先生は 私たちに\N何を伝えようとしているのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:27.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the instructor\N is trying to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:36.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,プロテイ～ン\N（エコー）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:43.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NWhich one to sing? What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっと どうしようかな\N何歌おうかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようかな どうしようかな\N（ゴリ）烈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:48.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko...\NThat's enough. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,もういいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,貸しなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SEND
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:06.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デスメタルの音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:10.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\Nこのカラオケボックスは 私の聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:10.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,These karaoke rooms\Nare my sanctuary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,REQUEST RECEIVED
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:17.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私が本当の自分でいられる\N秘密の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:16.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,where I can be my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:22.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だから 誰にも見られちゃいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:22.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...\NI have to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:27.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと そう信じてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:27.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've always believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:35.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子の叫び声）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I ever sing! This is my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:48.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,All death metal 'cause it makes me whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Metal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:57.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Death metal forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:58.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:10.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）オッ オッ オッ オ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）あああ～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:14.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll hurt your throat doing it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなやり方じゃ 喉 痛めますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,もっと しっかり 声帯を閉じて…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Clench your vocal chords, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ウアアアアアア！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だから 声帯を閉じるって何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, how do you\N"clench" the vocal chords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）ぜんっぜん意味分かんない\N（烈子）あ～…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:29.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）あと10分で終了時間です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:33.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Your time is up in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ･鷲美）んっ んっ んっ ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ウフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Extend it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:41.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,延長 お願いしまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitle translation: John Haguewood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:46.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:10.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
